Title: American Pie Presents: Band Camp
Actors: Eugene Levy, Tad Hilgenbrink, Arielle Kebbel, Jason Earles
Plot: Matt Stifler wants to be just like his big bro, making porn movies and having a good time in college. After sabotaging the school band, he gets sent to band camp where he really doesn't like it at first but then learns how to deal with the bandeez.
